Name: Dungeon Painter Studio
About the game: Dungeon Painter Studio is a powerful encounter map design tool, with a lot of features: Tilesets for indoor, outdoor and world maps Easy export to roll20, Fantasy Grounds, Tabletop Simulator and other VTT Layers and groups All objects are editable Union and subtraction operations Customizable filters (Drop Shadow, Glow, Bevel, Tint...) Easy import of custom art Sketchs import One click D20 random generator dungeons import Export to multipage pdf for print 1 inch, 1.5 inch & 1 cm grids A4, A3 and US Letter page Square and hex grid types
